summary:
...EVEN AS FRANCINE DISSIPATES A HEAVY RAINFALL AND FLASH FLOOD THREAT WILL CONTINUE ACROSS PORTIONS OF THE TENNESSEE VALLEY AND SOUTHEAST TONIGHT INTO SATURDAY...
